  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PunchBots is a game for up to 4 players. Compete with your friends while you play on the couch or practice against bots.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with a keyboard and controller is easy to learn like no other game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/6b25a57c967823a7bc15978f82e7a246.poster.avif?t=1768843157\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/6b25a57c967823a7bc15978f82e7a246.webm?t=1768843157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/6b25a57c967823a7bc15978f82e7a246.mp4?t=1768843157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Among the Main Features Are:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 different areas to choose from where you can face your friends with a total of 18 different arenas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Different power ups that you will find during the gameplay (rocket fists, extra speed, double fists, others)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The possibility of adding bots to complete the fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A test area to learn the basic controls and power ups of the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow us in our Discord community for news and development progress.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/f675addae5b94574ff4f97250fe35189.avif?t=1768843157\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PunchBots is a game for up to 4 players. Compete with your friends while you play on the couch or practice against bots.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with a keyboard and controller is easy to learn like no other game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/6b25a57c967823a7bc15978f82e7a246.poster.avif?t=1768843157\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/6b25a57c967823a7bc15978f82e7a246.webm?t=1768843157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/6b25a57c967823a7bc15978f82e7a246.mp4?t=1768843157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Among the Main Features Are:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 different areas to choose from where you can face your friends with a total of 18 different arenas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Different power ups that you will find during the gameplay (rocket fists, extra speed, double fists, others)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The possibility of adding bots to complete the fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A test area to learn the basic controls and power ups of the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Follow us in our Discord community for news and development progress.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2089170/extras/f675addae5b94574ff4f97250fe35189.avif?t=1768843157\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p>"